                <h1>Discovering Elijah in the Bible: Key Scriptures</h1>
                <p>Elijah is a significant prophet in the Bible, primarily featured in the books of 1 Kings and 2 Kings. He is known for his confrontation with King Ahab, his miraculous deeds, and his ascension to heaven in a whirlwind. Elijah exemplifies faith and divine power, serving as an essential figure in both Judaism and Christianity.</p>
